Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这 舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔洛克舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔刚蒂亚需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我过于沉重…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到能挺起胸膛向你父亲做出交待为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团长！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团长…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认地球的位置坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已根据银河同盟的标准坐标确定当前位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够归队了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归需要借助超光速飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 仅凭本机无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救信号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机紧急迫降到地球后发出的最初信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达银河同盟大约需要6582年16小时20分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论 回归大部队事实上不具备可操作性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:24.10,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}腾空而起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:30.32,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}梦想的尽头通向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:37.20,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}世界正待我们去探寻
